This project contains early firmware for the Kuongshun AD177 Turtle Robot using an ESP32. The code is modular, separating motors and line sensors, and implements basic line avoidance logic.

Note: The code is a work in progress and not yet complete. Further improvements and behaviors will be added.

Features (so far):
- Forward and backward movement based on the center line sensor.
- Motor control using PWM for smoother speed management.
- Modular structure for easier development.